reviewText:
Good storyline in this Buck Jones movie,really enjoyable. Picture & sound quality excellent. If you are a Jones fan then you cannot go wrong with this
dvd. Recommended.
Very high quality video. Many times these older films lose quality as they are copied over and over. The audio and video are exceptional in this version of California Trail.
All fans of "B" Westerns will love this one!  One of Buck's really good early Columbia films, from one of the greatest cowboys to ride the silver screen.
